content: "次元を超越した" (jigen wo chōetsu shita) is a phrase in Japanese that literally means "transcended dimensions". It is often used to describe something or someone that has exceeded or surpassed the boundaries or limitations of their respective field or category. For example, a work of art or a person's abilities that are considered to be "out of this world" or "extraordinary" would be described as "次元を超越した".
